OL,3,CCouple recreate wedding day picture on
OL,4,C65th anniversary
OL,6,FA couple from Cornwall who share a
OL,7,Flove of trains have celebrated their
OL,8,Fwedding anniversary in style.
OL,10,FAs a young girl, Margaret Stone used
OL,11,Fto wave at trains travelling from
OL,12,FLondon to Penzance.
OL,14,FOn the day of her wedding to George,
OL,15,FMargaret presented railway staff with
OL,16,Fa specially-made cake.
