OL,3,CCouple recreate wedding day picture on
OL,4,C65th anniversary
OL,6,FTo mark their 65th anniversary, Great
OL,7,FWestern Rail returned the favour,
OL,8,Fpresenting Margaret and George - who
OL,9,Fnow live in Carbis Bay - with a cake
OL,10,Fof their own.
OL,12,FMargaret and George tied the knot at
OL,13,Fher family farm in Wiltshire in
OL,14,FSeptember 1959.
OL,16,F"The train used to go through the
OL,17,Ffarm, and we lived higher than the
OL,18,Frailway," Margaret said. "And my
OL,19,Fsister and I used to wave, just like
OL,20,Fchildren do when a train goes by.
