OL,3,CCouple recreate wedding day picture on
OL,4,C65th anniversary
OL,6,F"Somebody told them we were getting
OL,7,Fmarried and the wedding reception was
OL,8,Fon the farm, and they really went very
OL,9,Fslowly and did lots of 'toot-tooting'
OL,10,Fand it was lovely."
OL,12,FGeorge said he was surprised to be the
OL,13,Fcentre of attention once more.
OL,15,F"65 years is a long time isn't it," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "She has looked after me for 65
OL,17,Fyears."
OL,19,FThe couple's daughter, Annette, said:
OL,20,F"We're so grateful to GWR for taking
OL,21,Fsuch an interest in my parents' story.
