OL,3,CCouple recreate wedding day picture on
OL,4,C65th anniversary
OL,6,F"Mum spent her childhood waving at the
OL,7,Ftrains and it's charming to see how
OL,8,Fshe developed such a bond with the
OL,9,Fdrivers and firemen.
OL,11,F"65 years of marriage is something
OL,12,Ftruly special to celebrate and today's
OL,13,Fpresentation really has been the icing
OL,14,Fon the cake for mum and dad."
OL,16,FDaniel Lloyd, from GWR, said: "It was
OL,17,Ffantastic to talk to George and
OL,18,FMargaret about their history of living
OL,19,Fclose to the railway line, whether
OL,20,Fthat was up in Wiltshire 65 years ago
OL,21,For here down in Cornwall today.
